{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"substring","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n</p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT#referencia_de_xslt.2fxpath\">Referencia de XSLT y XPath</a></b>: <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">Elementos XSLT</a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/EXSLT\">Funciones EXSLT</a>, <ahref=\" es=\"\" docs=\"\" web=\"\" xpath=\"\" funciones\"=\"\">XPath:Funciones, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath:Ejes</a>\n</ahref=\"></div>\n<p></p><p><br>\nLa función <code>substring</code> devuelve una parte de una cadena dada.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":" Sintaxis ","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">substring( <i>string</i> , <i>start</i> [, <i>length</i>] )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"argumentos","title":" Argumentos ","isH3":true,"content":"<dl><dt id=\"string\"><i><code>string</code></i> </dt><dd>La cadena a evaluar.\n</dd></dl>\n<dl><dt id=\"start\"><i><code>start</code></i>\n</dt><dd>La posición dentro de <i><code>string</code></i> donde comienza la subcadena.\n</dd></dl>\n<dl><dt id=\"length\"><i><code>length</code></i> (opcional)\n</dt><dd>La longitud de la subcadena. Si se omite, la cadena devuelta contendrá todos los carácteres desde la posición <i><code>start</code></i> hasta el final de <i><code>string</code></i>.\n</dd></dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"devuelve","title":" Devuelve ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Una cadena.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas","title":" Notas ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Como en otras funciones XPath, la posición no está basada en cero. El primer carácter de la cadena tiene la posición 1, no 0.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"definido","title":" Definido ","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-substring\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.2</a>\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"soporte_en_gecko","title":" Soporte en Gecko ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Soportado.\n</p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect2\">\n</div>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"La función substring devuelve una parte de una cadena dada.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"substring","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"substring","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"substring","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"substring","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"substring","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/xpath/functions/substring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/xpath/functions/substring/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Funciones"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/substring","title":"substring"}],"pageTitle":"substring - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}